replies.body:
{{champion:245}} 

He's just this abomination of a champion that does too much compared to most of the roster. His Q and W alone offer more than some champ's entire kits, which wouldn't be as much of a problem if he didn't do tons of damage. Also, due to how his kit and itemization work, he is impossible to shut down. 

AP bruisers have always been problematic in this game. Then it's like Riot just completely forgets that and creates this monster.

{{champion:7}}

I ban her 100% of the time. I don't care what lane I'm playing or what champ. I don't care if it's ranked, norms or otherwise, I'm resolved to NEVER EVER see that bitch in any of my games ever again. The one good thing that would come with 10 bans is she would be permabanned in my games. Hell, that's a cause for celebration.

I'd main her myself and probably reach Gold easy but I really really hate champs that have terrible wave clear. I can never main champs with poor wave clear. Just not my style of champ.
